quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) uburongozi bwiwe kuva kera kandi twari tumuzi neza
  21,52,"Mugihe yabwira Se wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- mbega aya masanamu mwicarirako imisi yose muyasenga"
  21,53,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- twebwe twasanze basogokuru bacu bayasenga"
  21,54,"Nawe abishura ati:- ntankeka mwebwe hamwe nabaso banyu mwari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  21,55,"Nabo\tbamwishura\tbati:-\tmbega\twaje\tngaha\tufise\tamajambo\ty’ukuri canke uri mubantu bafyinata"
  21,56,"Nawe\tabishura\tati:-\tahubwo\tUmuremyi\twanyu\tn’urya\tmuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi yayaremye, nanje ndi muvyabona vyemeza ibi vyose"
  21,57,Ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana yuko jewe nzoyagirira nabi aya masanamu yanyu nimwampa umugongo mugenda iyo mugenda
  21,58,"Rero aca arasenyura yamasanamu yose ayagira ibimanyu manyu, asigaza ryasanamu rininiya muriyo kugira ngo barisubire mwo"
  21,59,"Bagarutse bavuze bati:- ni nde yagize gutya izi Mana zacu? Mu vy’ukuri uyu muntu ari mubahemu bakuru"
  21,60,"Baca bavuga bati:- twumvise umusore umwe yitwa Ibrahiimu (iii)"
  21,61,"Bati:-\tnimu\tmurengutse\timbere\ty’amaso\ty’ishengero\try’abantu bamubone neza kumabi yiwe"
  21,62,"Bavuga\tbati:-\tmbega\tni\twewe\twagize\tgutya\tizi\tMana\tzacu\twewe Ibrahimu"
  21,63,"Nawe abishura ati:- Oya! uwabigize gutyo n’iri sanamu rikuru ryabo, rero nimuribaze yuko ashobora kuvuga kubijanye n’ibi bintu"
  21,64,"Baca\tbisubirako\tbabaza\timitima\tyabo\tnukuvuga\tbati:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri mwebwe mwamye muhemukira imitima yanyu"
  21,65,"Hanyuma baca bunamika imitwe y’abo hasi bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri uramaze kumenya yuko aya masanamu atavuga n’ikintu nakimwe"
  21,66,"Abishura ati:- mbega mwebwe musenga iyitari Imana ataco ibamarira n’ikintu na kimwe kandi ata nabi ibagirira"
  21,67,"Nimuceceke\tnivyo\tmusenga\tbiteye\tkubiri\tn’amasengesho\ty’Imana, mbega mwebwe ntimutegera"
  21,68,"Bavuga bati:- nimu muturire n’umucanwa kugira ngo murokore Imana zanyu nimwaba mwebwe muri mubagira ikintu nyaco"
  21,69,"Natwe duca tuvuga duti:- wa mukomezwa we! nube imbeho n’amahoro kubera intumwa y’Imana Ibrahiimu (iii)"
  21,70,Bamusabiye inabi mugabo twaciye tubagira kuba aribo bene uruhombo
  21,71,Duca turamurokora hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) tubajana mukindi gisagara twahezagiye kubera abantu bose
  21,72,"Nayo intumwa y’Imana Ibrahiimu (iii) twamuhaye ikibondo citiriwe izina rya Is’haqa (iii) hamwe n’uwundi yitwa Ya’aqubu (iii) kuba ariwe mwuzukuru wiwe, na bose twaciye tubagira kuba ari abantu beranda"
  21,73,"Hanyuma turaba hezagira kuba indongozi ziyobora abandi bantu kw’itegeko ryacu, nukuba rungikira ubutumwa nukuba bwereka nukugira ineza hamwe n’uguhagarika amasengesho hamwe n’ugutanga imperezwa, kandi iwacu bamye ari abantu batu gamburukira"
  21,74,"Intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) twaramuhaye amategeko n’ubumenyi nukumurokora n’abantu b’ico gisagara camye kigira amarorerwa mabi cane, ntankeka abo bantu bari abantu babi cane basenyura amategeko y’Imana"
  21,75,"Duca twinjiza iyo ntumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) mumihezagiro yacu, mu vy’ukuri yari mubagira ineza"